invalid type: string "Project Proposal: AI-Based Smart Attendance System\nObjective: Automate attendance using facial recognition and cloud storage. The system captures\nclassroom images, recognizes students, and updates attendance automatically. Technologies\ninclude Python, OpenCV, Flask, and MySQL. Expected benefits are reduced manual effort,\nimproved accuracy, and real-time tracking."˙˙˙˙˙˙˙˙